### Get All Brands
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/brands
Accept: application/json

### Get Brand by ID
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/brands/1
Accept: application/json

### Get Brands by Category
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/brands/category/1
Accept: application/json

### Create Brand (Admin)
POST {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/brands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Apple",
  "status": "active"
}

### Update Brand (Admin)
PUT {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/brands/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Apple Inc",
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete Brand (Admin)
DELETE {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/brands/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
